content: So glad he got a better platform here now was hard to find his Android apps for awhile now. This guy is simply the best. I first tried the free power nap one and bought this is my favorite one! Been using him since my first iPhone 3G back in the day!
Must have! Great for 'active' kids. I use it all the time and have for years.
Great app listen every night at bed time.
Been using its for about 10 years Thanx Andrew
Life changing! Andrew is the very best!
works for me

I absolutely cannot fall asleep.wothout using at least one of Andrew's apps. when I am having severe sleep issues, I use Deep Sleep. if I start feeling like I'm sliding into binge eating, I'll use Lose Weight. I used Stop Drinking to help my alcohol addiction. Recently, I have been using Positivity to battle some depression.
Waking up daily with a positive outlook..amazing app.
Incredibly relaxing and oddly energising at the same time. Helping me through a challenging period. Would highly recommend.
Excellent settings continuous sessions of your choose ending with sleep or wake up and words spoken non invasive non threatening wording .so easy to let go into relaxation state of mind
Great app, but there is no option to move to external SD. Otherwise good app.

I cannot say enough wonderful things about this app and the other meditation apps like it. The adjustability of the programming is fantastic, Andrew Johnson's voice is magical. I fell asleep listening to it just about every night , even bought special sleeping headphones to wear just so I could use this app. I highly recommend this app and others like it for just about an ailment you have in your life. Get Good quality sleep! And meditate! It will change your life.

Mr. Andrew Johnson thank you so much for helping me throughout the years to 
recover and become a better person I've been using your therapy for 6 years 
now and I absolutely love it. Nothing else worked for me except for your 
therapy thank you again and God bless you
Favourite sleep app!!
Perfect way to start my day!

I personally liked it but when I upgraded to family Google account it says it's eligible for moving to the family library but won't let me do so, uninstalled and reinstalled and everything, no go. Please fix and I'm happily put back to 5 star!

Wow. This may be the best money I've ever spent. Super fan. This is the most relaxing voice you'll ever hear. I love the affirmations. Great for self confidence, mood, anxiety, feelings of helplessness, or stress. Please treat yourself to this.

I was skeptical at first... been using app for a few weeks now and I feel like my coping mechanisms have improved and I'm feeling more confident in myself. Also think I'm more content and more grateful. Thanks so much. Life changing

Wow!!! Thank you Andrew. You have possibly saved my life i have been in a really dark place i have used this app for a week now and im already on the up and up im feeling really good already. The universe put ot to the test this morning i was in a minor car accident and although i was shaken i was still happy and positive about life which surprised me and those close to me. Thank you so much for helping me see the positive in life. Thank you thank you thank you.
Not enough options for meditations.
Best set of apps like this I have ever used. Effective !!!
Love it! His voice and scripts are wonderful.
I like the app but there is a whole lot of noise in the recording . It's very annoying,  especially when listening at a low level. Please re-record it and give us an update.
His voice is soothing, everyone I play it for loves it. The message is unique.
I adore his voice. It as very soothing.
How the heck do you close the app?  A simple X in upper corner would be nice
Love this however adjusting the volume takes my phone off silent and the short induction takes me down into sleep despite choosing awaken at the start.
Fantastic
Really the only thing i can sleep soundly to
These meditations are perfect for relaxing at the end of the day and getting a positive focus for tomorrow.
It really works.
This guy is so so good. I love his voice and how he makes the whole world around you disappear so you only focus on his voice. So helpful!  xxxxx

This application is very relaxing. Andrew Johnson has this incredibly calming voice. I find I drift off to sleep and I absorb the messages subliminally whilst I'm asleep. In past I've had nights where I just can't drift off or as soon as I do I anxiously worry about things that aren't necessary. I used this application after three major incidents. Usually I would spiral into self destruct mode but I'm finding that I have a much more positive  outlook on life and I'm much happier in general.
I love this app. It has helped me so much when I use it consistently!

I have Chronic Daily Migraines & I was going through a hospital Migraine Clinic and in they have a Biofeedback program, but I used Andrew's meditation apps (I have them all! Instead of their preprogrammed one's.
Life saver ;) I mean it..

Great app to get you out of negative thinking and habits which can cause depression, anger and sadness. It has helped me tremendously in the past with issues but I still listen to it at times to keep me on track when I feel bit down, anxious or in a negative rut. His soothing voice is hypnotic alone.
A few of the reviews spoke of sound editing problems, I'm happy to say that there are none in this version. Just got this one and it is up to the high level I've seen in his other apps.
Intro built on practices used in his other meditations. Invigorating.
Really great the make you relax fall asleep and you will wake up in a more positive way.
Good app. Andrews voice well suited to the task but very poor editing. Shame.
Fantastic
Please remove the music from the scripts. It's unpleasant and discourages some users people from actually using the app.

I used this as a follow up app, where I first used the " move on " app to deal with some bad feelings that surfaced after a miscarriage.(Regrets and guilt from the past). This one is the one that smoothed the rawness over for me. I also gifted this to my sister. She slept well, but always was tense and stressed. I felt her self esteem was low, and this app she says does help her (sleep) relaxed. I think there should be more of these, I own so many, it feels like I got serious issues :-)
Wish the interface was as sophisticated as the one for apple.
Wonderfully soothing and uplifting. I have bipolar and Andrews aps have helped me cope while cutting back my medication.

I have a few of his programs and I like them. This one however, is the weakest of the 5 I've purchased. The statements are too general, unlike his other programs (which are usually very specific, well thought out statements). I recommend "build confidence" over this one.

I bought this app a few days ago and listened to it a few times. The editing is really bad. Sound cuts off and even one part is exactly repeated. At one point when he asks to press two fingers against each other, he says he will ask it again later on but it never happens! The app is supposed to make it easy to concentrate but is not. Please fix the audio editing.
Love them all and I have a few

I like each of the programs Andrew has.. Each word he speaks I let it become apart of myself.. In my opinion he is really good at guiding you into a relaxed state.. I always fall asleep or feel a lot better after listening. Definitely worth it. Thanks Andrew.
Andrew Johnson has spoiled me! Ii cant listen to any other recorded hypnotherapists. Thanks!

This is such a soothing app. I sometimes have difficulty falling asleep and this app is great! Andrew's voice is so relaxing, I feel completely at peace when listening to this after a long day. I find when I listen TO this app at night, I wake up literally feeling more positive. Total believer!
this is the first of andrews apps i have used, it is well worth the money, i have downloaded almost all of them since.. thank you.
Sounds like it was pieced together but still does the job
Worth every penny!!

When turning off the screen to make the screen blank the audio cuts off! Please change this as some of the apps have this function & its so much better...would be a 5* if so! That aside fab work its great!!

I have several of his recordings, this is one of my favorites. Recommend it... Andrew Johnson's voice is very relaxing. I recommend any of his products. I have several of his relaxation tapes and they work! He is also great about answering emails if you have questions; he is a true professional and believes 100% in what he is doing.
All of these are great.... They can be saved to SD and really effective for relaxing! Only downside is if the android phone doesn't have enough space for apps.

This is a great meditation with a truly skilled and comforting male voice as a guide. I found myself relaxed and inspired.  I especially like the customization options that allow you to adjust the length of the meditation and tailor it to going to sleep or waking up at the end.  This will definitely be a valuable tool in my quest to bring more optimism into my life.
You will love this app.
It works!
I have other of his apps, LOVE THEM. This one has the longest pauses in between sessions, it isn't constructed as well and it disappoints me. Still a fan of Andrew but this one should be updated!!

I'm quite skeptical of this stuff but recently found myself in a deep depression due to life circumstances. I felt no hope and was feeling very insecure.  I was willing to give anything a shot because I do not like taking medication for stuff like that.  I tried this one night before bed,  fell asleep midway, but woke up with an odd sense of happiness and general feeling of "everything is fine". I know this helped me,  I use this every night since and it just gets better every day! Thank you!!

I always fall asleep during the introduction when listening to it in bed so have to use actual content when I'm on the train and not as relaxed and open to subliminal suggestion but it still works a bit like CBT in that it makes me think what I could do to make the statements on the recording a reality,  which is great! Worth the relatively low cost of under Â£2.

several obvious breaks where audio clips weren't blended well, says the same thing twice, fingers pressed but no reason why and never mentions again.  Seems like they tried to make more money w/out actually recording a new track.
Very relaxing. Nicely paced. My favorite so far.
I love it can't sleep without him, helped me from my anger and suicidal thoughts, thank you Andrew you saved my life

I don't usually review apps but this one is worth it. I fall asleep before the end almost every night! The best way I can describe his voice would be if Sean Connery and Bob Ross had a baby...LOVE IT!  $2.99 is not too much to pay for the best sleep I've ever experienced.
Add 1 star for update. Emails still unanswered. Find user interface restrictive. Effectiveness uncertain. Relatively pricey!
Great voice, great app.

Downloaded w/o any issues.  Runs as expected.  Been listening to it for a few days, and it appears to be therapeutic and no doubt a nice dose of "positive" in my otherwise hectic life.  Simple, effective and inexpensive.
Always makes me feel good about myself and relaxes me
Love it
Great customer service! Awesome product!
This program has helped me so much and really appreciate your understanding of what people such as myself needs. Thank you so very much.
What does the update do?
Just listened for first time, very soothing and relaxing, definitely feel calmer.
Great app!
it would be great if i can optionally turn off the voice.
.... if there was a 'move to SD' option. Still a good app but though. Come on Andrew, tweak it a little bit will ya?
Love it! Made me feel better.
AJ makes the best apps in this genre
I have all of Andrew's apps each and every one of them has help me and my family...
Cant live without this app love all his apps . He also has a facebook page that is very helpful
2nd app from you that hasn't downloaded :( refund
this is my second app from andrew. the first one i got was the deep sleep. that was fine. however, this app wont finish downloading. neee to refund
It feels natural. It feels comfortable.
Good worth the money
Noticed that i was being positive woke up feeling good talked positive, good things happened. You saved my life andrew thank u
This REALLY WORKS! I bought most of these & plan to buy more...
Woke up in the best mood!
Very relaxing. Enjoy listening to his voice.
Rarely buy apps. Now proud owner/regular user of 10 from his series. No Regrets. Do regret every single other purchase same category. Well done. Thx
Wouldn't download. Got refund.
My fav to sleep to, relaxing.
Amazing. Andrew's programs are definitely worth the $3. I have 5 of them, and listen to them before bed!
Love it
Start every day with this app, you will love it.
Amazing app. Great relaxation, however I fall asleep before finishing the audio. I dream better and get better sleep. I'll have to try during the day.
Great app but not for me.
Smoking weed and listening to his apps is the best medication and therapy.
Amazing. Put me to sleep and made me feel happier! Must download!
I love this app; puts me in a nice mood and reduces stress. So far, this is the only app I've bothered to buy again when moving from iTouch to Droid
I have 10 of his apps and love them all!!!!
Content missing on app. Force quit alot
This really helps me after a super frustrating day at work. I luv the hivebrain/ Andrew apps.
Great program! Downloads in no time at all on the motorola droid
It won't even bein downloading??
